title: 1995 IGA Classic – Singles
text:
<a href="Meredith%20McGrath">Meredith McGrath</a> was the defending champion but did not compete that year.
<a href="Brenda%20Schultz-McCarthy">Brenda Schultz</a> won in the final 6–1, 6–2 against <a href="Elena%20Likhovtseva">Elena Likhovtseva</a>.
Seeds.
A champion seed is indicated in bold text while text in italics indicates the round in which that seed was eliminated.
